    <article class="content--container">
        <p>
            <b>Sarah</b> (she/her) and <b>Quin</b> (he/him) warmly welcome you to Bluey & Co., a community-inspired cafe featuring Asian beverages and desserts with a nostalgic twist. At Bluey & Co., we've gained renown for our unique tiramisu creations – from the richness of injeolmi (인절미) to the delightful combination of <b>matcha with red bean</b>, and the comforting familiarity of <b>banana milk</b> and <b>k-coffee biscoff</b>. Inspired by the essence of "tiramisu," translated as "pick me up," resonates profoundly with us, especially in light of the challenges posed by the COVID era, we've crafted our treats to be a thoughtful remedy, striking the perfect <b>balance of sweetness</b> without overwhelming the palate.
        </p>
        <p>
            Beyond our signature tiramisu, our menu features a selection of nostalgic <b>Asian-flavored beverages</b> that really hit the spot. They will definitely transport you back to warm fond memories with every sip!
        </p>
        <p>
            However, Bluey & Co. is not just about the food and drinks. We offer the sense of community, the laughter, and the meaningful connections, over a cup of coffee. Come by to our pop-up cafe for <b>good coffee and better company!</b>
        </p>      
